"Vehicle" means any vehicle registered in this State as:
A Class E (truck) vehicle with a registered, operating, or rated gross vehicle weight of over 10,000 pounds;
A Class F (tractor) vehicle;
A Class G (trailer or semitrailer) vehicle with a registered, operating, or rated gross vehicle weight over 10,000 pounds;
A Class P (passenger bus) vehicle; or
A Class M (multipurpose) vehicle that:
Is used primarily to transport passengers; and
Is designed to transport 16 passengers or more, including the driver; or
Was previously registered under § 13-932 or § 13-933 of this article.
